# Use cases
- File transfer
- Package Management
- Users and groups management
- Managing services
- Fact gathering
- General System Information
- Software deployment by Git
- Playbook creation testing

# Examples
# ansible host -i inventory_file -m module -a "arguments"
# ansible -i inventory/inventory.ini all -m ping
# ansible host_1 -i inventory/inventory.ini -m setup 
# ansible host_2 -i inventory/inventory.ini -m copy -a "src=home/user_name/ansible/file_to_copy dest=/tmp"
# anssible host_2 -a "ls -l /tmp"